{"tid":1757973,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"大食撚平均一日食$80算唔算慳錢","createTime":"2019-11-26T20:36:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T09:27:29.000Z","uid":238361,"like":507,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":98,"replies":[{"pid":"927f007acc2946c2e2e089b69e111414de27798b","tid":1757973,"uid":238361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T20:36:43.000Z","msg":"出咗嚟住，冇屋企飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我大食到一餐自己煮雙營多腸仔蛋水餃都要三十幾蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，食營多杯麵烏冬食到反胃，唯有多啲出街食啦，KFC下午茶用曬優惠券都要$60一餐先飽飽地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唯有間中食1.5餐，先做到平均一日$80<br />\n我咁樣算唔算慳錢，定其實我咁樣算大洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：慳錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：大洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b5d9c33ffd277ef897804324e24d5f1ea83effe","tid":1757973,"uid":4139,"like":138,"dislike":3,"score":135,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T20:46:19.000Z","msg":"$80梗係慳啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出去食個飯都5060"},{"pid":"9454f5c45157c4dad9fa0927596902f0f7e7c1b2","tid":1757973,"uid":251336,"like":10,"dislike":160,"score":-150,"quote":{"pid":"5b5d9c33ffd277ef897804324e24d5f1ea83effe","tid":1757973,"uid":4139,"like":138,"dislike":3,"score":135,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T20:46:19.000Z","msg":"$80梗係慳啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出去食個飯都5060"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T21:03:1