kgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好再食即食野啦, 求其都起碼買D肥牛羊淥米粉食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c64f444662cb54da583fdc02e775b9dd140678ec","tid":1757973,"uid":273587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T15:14:51.000Z","msg":"80蚊可以食到好多野喎<br />\n睇你點洗嘅啫<br />\n不過其實自己煮一定係最抵"},{"pid":"782992289db5da27d272b140d0798532c9d85c78","tid":1757973,"uid":273587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c316469c5fec8037171e74c0c9142b43a04cdca","tid":1757973,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4113b1b41a07627beb295acd3c7d04f25983adac","tid":1757973,"uid":173011,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T23:15:24.000Z","msg":"我一日三餐自己煮，每日買餸錢控制30蚊以內<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T03:55:23.000Z","msg":"有冇餸單推介"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T15:21:09.000Z","msg":"麻婆豆腐($10蚊肉碎、4蚊豆腐)<br />\n炒雜菌($3金針菇、$5杏鮑菇、$10鴻喜菇)<br />\n蒸水蛋($4雞蛋)"},{"pid":"33801a9b445902f04ba866967023b54b84588a7b","tid":1757973,"uid":173011,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2c316469c5fec8037171e74c0c9142b43a04cdca","tid":1757973,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4113b1b41a07627beb295acd3c7d04f25983adac","tid":1757973,"uid":173011,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T23:15:24.000Z","msg":"我一日三餐自己煮，每日買餸錢控制30蚊以內<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T03:55:23.000Z","msg":"有冇餸單推介"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T15:30:44.000Z","msg":"薯仔絲煎蛋<br />\n蕃茄炒蛋+急凍三色豆<br />\n佳寶買急凍蜆肉(好平)，可以炆冬瓜/炆節瓜/炆豆腐<br />\n肉碎煮豆腐<br />\n肉碎炆茄子<br />\n青瓜煮雲耳<br />\n雞絲(急凍雞扒)抄西芹、炒青瓜<br />\n洋蔥炒雞柳(急凍雞扒)<br />\n豆豉鯪魚的魚肉炒油麥菜，多出的油豆豉再用來炒苦瓜<br />\n10蚊鯪魚肉，5蚊用來煎蛋，5蚊用來釀青椒<br />\n蟹柳蒸水蛋<br />\n<br />\n窮撚餐肉類會較少，但有時煎多隻蛋就可以補充蛋白質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/